|                                          |
|    Masters Thesis for Simon J. Potter    |
|                                          |
--------------------------------------------


Requirements:
-------------

This thesis requires:

    + Inkscape
    + pdflatex and several LaTeX packages:

        - babel
        - booktabs
        - caption
        - color
        - float
        - fontenc
        - geometry
        - graphicx
        - grffile
        - hypernat
        - hyperref
        - inputenc
        - microtype
        - natbib
        - parskip
        - pgf
        - subcaption
        - tikz
        - titlesec

      Most of these packages will be available by default with any texlive
      installation on Linux.

    + python-pygments (for code listings)
    + R (at least 2.15)
    + Sweave


Usage:
------

In order to generate the resulting report.pdf file simply run `make`.
